additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Longevity varies widely depending on temperature, fan speed, air flow and driving time. Do not place this product in direct sunlight. Note: Clip must be over vents blade, not between blades. Prolonged exposure to high interior temperatures must be avoided. If the outside temperature exceeds 35 degrees Celsius, remove air freshener from vehicle and store in a sealed container to avoid leakage or damage. Notice: This product contains parts that may pose a choking hazard. For adults use only. Product is not a toy.
